<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>أَجَابَهُ إِنْ كَانَ ظَنيِّ صَادِقَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَإِنَّني قَاضِي القُضَاةِ سَابِقَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{أَمِيرُ الشُّعَرَاء / أَحْمَد شَوْقِي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>خُذْ بِيَدِي اليَوْم؛ آخُذُ بِرِجْلِكَ غَدَاً<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>حِكَايَةُ الكَلْبِ مَعَ الحَمَامَة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تَشْهَدُ لِلْجِنْسَيْنِ بِالكَرَامَة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يُقَالُ كَانَ الكَلبُ ذَاتَ يَوْمِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بَيْنَ الرِّيَاضِ غَارِقَاً في النَّوْمِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَجَاءَ مِنْ وَرَائِهِ الثُّعْبَانُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>مُنْتَفِخَاً كَأَنَّهُ الشَّيْطَانُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَهَمَّ أَنْ يَغْدِرَ بِالأَمِينِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَرَقَّتِ الوَرْقَاءُ لِلْمِسْكِينِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَنَزَلَتْ حَتىَّ تُغِيثَ الكَلْبَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَنَقَرَتْهُ نَقْرَةً فَهَبَّا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَحَمِدَ اللَّهَ عَلَى السَّلاَمَة<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَحَفِظَ الجَمِيلَ لِلْحَمَامَة<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَمَرَّ مَا مَرَّ مِنَ الزَّمَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَجَاءَ صَيادُونَ لِلْمَكَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَصَوَّبُواْ نحْوَ الحَمَامَةِ السِّلاَحْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَنَبَّهَ الكَلْبُ الوَرْقَاءَ بِالنُّبَاحْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>